   123	- **INCONCLUSIVE** ⇒ escalate (grow N or accept) — do not act on an underpowered split.
   124	Feeds the Slice-30 resolution + the 0.8.4 (GraphRAG) / HippoRAG sequencing. **Not** a causal proof —
