The reused harness gives identical prompt/reader routing, but it currently has no context fitter at all: it joins every hit body in full. That matters because the design relies on “same 32k fitter as D0b,” so I’m checking branch-specific D0b runner/checkpoint code before deciding whether this doc has a real methodology gap or just an implementation reference gap.
