   190	    priced call** — so it can be re-derived from a saved artifact (the model was
   191	    corrected after the priced pilot; this lets the artifact be regenerated for
   192	    free). Returns P(GO) at the pilot N for each effect shape, the required N for
   193	    P(GO) ≥ 0.8 under flat-positive (+ a rho-sensitivity sweep), an on-corpus
   194	    feasibility verdict, and the projected $ for the full baseline pass.
